        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2024/0911-kamakura/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_0030.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_0030.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_0030.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_0030.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_0030"/></a></p>

